1. Create fragment layout >>> example_fragment

2. Create a java class that extends Fragment
        A. Override onCreateView method
        B. Inflate the layout created in step 1.
        C. Define the views inside onCreateView method.

3. In the activity insert the frame layout in the xml file.

4. To send values for the fragment we make a public static method with wanted parameters
        A. To save the values we used the Bundle.
        B. To show it .. onCreateView get the values with the same keys that saved in.